Hello Zach & Raffaella,
Thank you for the enquiry. I have received the response yesterday I had req=
uested from ASURNZ which clarifies the process for technical assessment and=
 expert opinion provided to Tower Insurance by ASURNZ.
Presently being in receipt of this clarification will now allow me to respo=
nd to the questions Rafaella has raised.
I will send through the response to within the next 2 days to allow for the=
 progression of the property assessment.
Kind Regards,
Grant.

[cid:image003.png@01DC32AF.6FC26A30]
